 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
 PROGRAM-ID. FIZZBUZZ.
 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
 DATA DIVISION.
 	WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
 		01 COUNTER PIC 9(5).
 		01 MAX PIC 9(5).
 		01 REM PIC 9(5).
 		01 TEMP PIC 9(5).		
 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
 PARA-1.
 	DISPLAY "ENTER MAX NUMBER: ". 
 	ACCEPT MAX.
	PERFORM VARYING COUNTER FROM 1 BY 1
		UNTIL COUNTER > MAX		
		DIVIDE COUNTER BY 3 GIVING TEMP REMAINDER REM
			IF REM = 0
				DIVIDE COUNTER BY 5 GIVING TEMP REMAINDER REM
					IF REM = 0
						DISPLAY "FIZZBUZZ"
					ELSE 
						DISPLAY "BUZZ"
					END-IF.
			END-IF.	
		DIVIDE COUNTER BY 3 GIVING TEMP REMAINDER REM
			IF REM = 0
				DISPLAY "FIZZ"
			ELSE 
				DISPLAY COUNTER
			END-IF.	 
	END-PERFORM
 STOP RUN.
 
